Text: In Games Workshop's "Warhammer Fantasy" and "Warhammer 40,000" fictional universes, Chaos refers to the malevolent entities which live in a different timespace, known as the Warp in "Warhammer 40,000" and as the Realm of Chaos in "Warhammer Fantasy".
